{"tid":1426091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實，而家先係我地收成期","createTime":"2019-08-07T00:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T01:28:38.000Z","uid":188176,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"207e785e63126968466d7d6538973e2b578c7acf","tid":1426091,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:44:02.000Z","msg":"其實一直以黎，我地太專注係播種(抗爭)既時期<br />\n而忽略左收成既時間<br />\n而家我地手上其實大把警犬醜態<br />\n但往往一時三刻就忘記左<br />\n最重要係忘記左個憤怒<br />\n所以面家最重要係整理工作同文宣<br />\n我地要有系統同有條理咁整理警犬濫權既事件，一件事一個log<br />\n一個log包括片，圖同文，要做到有qa有管理<br />\n之後先可以方便文宣，如民間記者會做野同文宣組制作poster<br />\n魚革失敗主要在於時代，人和輸七成<br />\n但而家天時地利係晒我地到<br />\n再失敗既話即係係香港人問題，代表香港人根本無資格抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地要做既係要用文宣去宣傳警犬點濫權<br />\n唔好再講矛頭指去警犬無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n警犬就係代表政府，佢地就係極權既表現體<br />\n文宣就係要香港人記住傷痛，要普通市民記住警犬帶比佢地既不安同恐懼<br />\n最後結果就係怒火，只有怒火先可以推動時代既巨輪<br />\n文宣唔可以再停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bdb14211a28d089301bfe918e230258814e294b","tid":1426091,"uid":222190,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:46:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BeOBtK4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBeOBtK4.png&h=f5198bc7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/084618_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F084618_ee9bd865176d0dc56b5be2ca89399833.png&h=4c0a9481&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/084619_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F084619_0f6641dea7107721bd03942237f5fc64.png&h=ffa20d32&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/084621_aadf0579c287a9304ec38c9ecbe0a2e9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F084621_aadf0579c287a9304ec38c9ecbe0a2e9.png&h=6d3b51fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/07/084622_0dccc94b7190dc5fb97749cfc3216e2b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F08%2F07%2F084622_0dccc94b7190dc5fb97749cfc3216e2b.png&h=86a443bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"567670f4f04a3873c41538257389ed0e896f3355","tid":1426091,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:51:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d746b5fe7eb6743f5191ed5b8a1f73facd798b7f","tid":1426091,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:56:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59151fb0b64380c5222d051b1eb1c8379dedc10b","tid":1426091,"uid":293901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:58:11.000Z","msg":"除左警方既不是。<br />\n可唔可以收集哩段時間入面，我地香港人點樣由之前「隔離左」既鄰舍，變成依家就算互不相識，都會彼此幫忙。互相打氣既片段？"},{"pid":"aa2305eb138eece434e0d203e3ba7fee2611046d","tid":1426091,"uid":293901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59151fb0b64380c5222d051b1eb1c8379dedc10b","tid":1426091,"uid":293901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:58:11.000Z","msg":"除左警方既不是。<br />\n可唔可以收集哩段時間入面，我地香港人點樣由之前「隔離左」既鄰舍，變成依家就算互不相識，都會彼此幫忙。互相打氣既片段？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T00:58:44.000Z","msg":"抗爭之中，我地係有愛。"},{"pid":"eaaf5225c54820a96ae36144ab01b73315d1df68","tid":1426091,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T01:05:14.000Z","msg":"係，之前啲長輩圖停晒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8198dfffafa4d137af18a496709ece704c3fd312","tid":1426091,"uid":235535,"like"